text: TV Rudo or Televizija Rudo is a local Bosnian public television channel based in Rudo municipality. It was established on 28 June 1993 as part of public municipality services. == References == == External links == * Official website of Rudo municipality * Website of CRA BiH Category:Television channels and stations established in 1993 Category:Television stations in Bosnia and Herzegovina
